text: Dan Humphrey is a fictional character from the critically acclaimed series The Vampire Diaries, starring Nina Dobrev (as Elena Gilbert), Paul Wesley (as Stefan Salvatore) and Penn Badgley (as Dan Humphrey). This character portrays a dark, twisted personality who yearns for the hunt and kill, but deep down, holds those he loves dearly (almost excessively) and would do anything to protect his precious lover (again, a little excessively...).
